азвертывания на устройствах. Построенная как модель Mixture-of-Experts с 24 миллиардами ', 'context': 32768, 'price_prompt': 3.04941e-06, 'price_completion': 1.219764e-05}, {'id': 'qwen/qwen-turbo', 'description': 'Qwen-Turbo, основанный на Qwen2.5, является моделью с контекстом 1M, обеспечивающей высокую скорость и низкую стоимость, подходящей для простых задач.', 'context': 131072, 'price_prompt': 3.3035275e-06, 'price_completion': 1.321411e-05}, {'id': 'amazon/nova-micro-v1', 'description': 'Amazon Nova Micro 1.0 — это текстовая модель, обеспечивающая наименьшую задержку ответов в семействе моделей Amazon Nova при очень низкой стоимости. С длиной контекста в 128 тысяч токенов и оптимизиро', 'context': 128000, 'price_prompt': 3.557645e-06, 'price_completion': 1.423058e-05}, {'id': 'cohere/command-r7b-12-2024', 'description': 'Command R7B (12-2024) является небольшим, быстрым обновлением модели Command R+, выпущенным в декабре 2024 года. Эта модель превосходно справляется с RAG, использованием инструментов, агентами и анало', 'context': 128000, 'price_prompt': 3.8117625e-06, 'price_completion': 1.524705e-05}]\n\nRequirements:\n- choose appropriate models\n- design agents\n- define tools\n- include execution loop if needed\n", type='TextMessage'), TextMessage(id='4a4c5374-7399-4f6f-95e8-0094541a5796', source='architect_agent', models_usage=RequestUsage(prompt_tokens=1969, completion_tokens=783), metadata={}, created_at=datetime.datetime(2026, 3, 31, 18, 29, 15, 699300, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), content='```json\n{\n  "system": {\n    "name": "WireGuard VPN Configuration and Network Troubleshooting System",\n    "description": "A multi-agent system to configure WireGuard VPN and troubleshoot network issues.",\n    "agents": [\n      {\n        "name": "ConfigurationAgent",\n        "description": "Agent responsible for configuring WireGuard VPN.",\n        "model": "qwen/qwen2.5-coder-7b-instruct",\n        "tools": [\n          {\n            "name": "WireGuardConfigurator",\n            "description": "Tool to generate and apply WireGuard VPN configurations."\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        "name": "TroubleshootingAgent",\n        "description": "Agent responsible for troubleshooting network issues.",\n        "model": "qwen/qwen3-vl-30b-a3b-thinking",\n        "tools": [\n          {\n            "name": "NetworkDiagnosticTool",\n            "description": "Tool to perform network diagnostics and identify issues."\n          },\n          {\n            "name": "LogAnalyzer",\n            "description": "Tool to analyze network logs for errors and anomalies."\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        "name": "SecurityAgent",\n        "description": "Agent responsible for ensuring security and compliance.",\n        "model": "meta-llama/llama-guard-3-8b",\n        "tools": [\n          {\n            "name": "SecurityScanner",\n            "description": "Tool to scan for security vulnerabilities and compliance issues."\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    "execution_loop": {\n      "steps": [\n        {\n          "step": 1,\n          "description": "ConfigurationAgent generates and applies WireGuard VPN configurations.",\n          "agent": "ConfigurationAgent",\n          "tool": "WireGuardConfigurator"\n        },\n        {\n          "step": 2,\n          "description": "TroubleshootingAgent performs network diagnostics and identifies issues.",\n          "agent": "TroubleshootingAgent",\n          "tool": "NetworkDiagnosticTool"\n        },\n        {\n          "step": 3,\n          "description": "TroubleshootingAgent analyzes network logs for errors and anomalies.",\n          "agent": "TroubleshootingAgent",\n          "tool": "LogAnalyzer"\n        },\n        {\n          "step": 4,\n          "description": "SecurityAgent scans for security vulnerabilities and compliance issues.",\n          "agent": "SecurityAgent",\n          "tool": "SecurityScanner"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n===EXPLANATION===\n\nThe system is designed to configure WireGuard VPN and troubleshoot network issues using a multi-agent approach. The system consists of three main agents: ConfigurationAgent, TroubleshootingAgent, and SecurityAgent. Each agent is equipped with specific tools to perform its designated tasks.\n\n1. **ConfigurationAgent**: This agent uses the Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct model to generate and apply WireGuard VPN configurations. It utilizes the WireGuardConfigurator tool for this purpose.\n\n2. **TroubleshootingAgent**: This agent uses the Qwen3-VL-30B-A3B-Thinking model to perform network diagnostics and identify issues. It employs the NetworkDiagnosticTool and LogAnalyzer tools to analyze network logs for errors and anomalies.\n\n3. **SecurityAgent**: This agent uses the Llama Guard 3-8B model to ensure security and compliance. It utilizes the SecurityScanner tool to scan for security vulnerabilities and compliance issues.\n\nThe execution loop defines the sequence of steps that the agents will follow to configure the WireGuard VPN and troubleshoot network issues. The loop includes steps for configuration, network diagnostics, log analysis, and security scanning. This ensures that the system can handle the tasks in a structured and efficient manner.', type='TextMessage')] stop_reason=None
